department: NADIMPALLI SATYANARAYANA RAJU INSTITUTE OF TECHNOLOGY (NSRIT AUTONOMOUS)
description: TECHNIMBLE 2025 is a technical fest organized by NSRIT, offering a platform for students to showcase their skills and knowledge through various events like Poster Presentation, Paper Presentation, Project Expo, Technical Quiz, Modeling & 3D Printing, Technical Treasure Hunt, Bridge Bust, B-Quiz, Ad-Mad, and Startup Idea competition. Participants stand a chance to win exciting prizes.
target_audience: Students from various engineering and management disciplines including CSE/CSD/CSM, ECE, MECH, EEE, CIVIL, MBA, and MCA.
additional_info: Registration can be done by scanning the provided QR code.
